original: Mama was engaged in cleaning activities, utilizing a large cord to shake and clean the room. By vigorously moving the cord back and forth, she successfully removed dirt from the room, resulting in a clean environment. Satisfied with her work, Mama stored the cord and exclaimed, "Finished!"
